<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />Long ago you spoke in a vision to your faithful ones;</para>

<para style="q1">you said, "I have set a crown on a mighty one;</para>

<para style="q1">I have raised up one chosen from among the people.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="20" style="v" />I have chosen David my servant;</para>

<para style="q1">with my holy oil have I anointed him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />My hand will support him;</para>

<para style="q1">my arm will strengthen him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="22" style="v" />No enemy will deceive him;</para>

<para style="q1">no son of wickedness will oppress him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="23" style="v" />I will crush his enemies before him;</para>

<para style="q1">I will kill those who hate him.</para>
